    <abstract>
      <t>In some multihoming SRv6 L3VPN and EVPN scenarios, there are
   requirements for the egress PE to advertise both unicast and anycast
   SRv6 Service SIDs for the same service. This document defines the
   Anycast-flag for SRv6 Service SIDs carried in BGP messages.</t>
    </abstract>
